119.question: Review
119.answer: When I firs received the sample, I thought maybe it was just  hopping on the cleansing conditioner bandwagon.  But I've used and liked other Tresemme products, so I was happy to give it a try. I was surprised how much I enjoyed this products. My hair felt clean and soft and the product did not leave any residue or greasy feeling afterwards.  I would try it again!
